        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1954-12-31T14:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1954-04-26T00:00:00-05:00" n="1109" subtype="editorial-note"
                type="document" xml:id="d1109">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>For text of <gloss target="#t_NSC1">NSC</gloss> 5429, “Review of U.S. Policy in
                    the Far East,” August 4, 1954, a report to the National Security Council by the
                    Planning Board, see <ref target="frus1952-54v12p1">volume XII</ref>. This
                    report, which included a section on Indochina, was approved (as amended) by the
                    Council at its 210th Meeting, August 12, 1954, as <gloss target="#t_NSC1"
                        >NSC</gloss> 5429/1. For extracts from the memorandum of discussion at the
                    210th Meeting of the <gloss target="#t_NSC1">NSC</gloss> and other documentation
                    relating to the <gloss target="#t_NSC1">NSC</gloss> 5429 series, see <ref
                        target="frus1952-54v12p1">
                        <hi rend="italic">ibid</hi>
                    </ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
